---++ <%= index %>. Explaination of Testcases.<br>---<br>
<% index = index + 1 %>
&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;* Here listed all testcases used by Beijing SQE team.<br>
&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;* All testcases are devied into 3 categories, "Info check", "Operation", "Stress".<br>
&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;* In each category, testcases are typed by the place in which cases are executed.<br>

<% tmptype = nil %>

---++ <%= index %>.Testcases of "Infomation Check".<br>---<br>
<% index = index + 1 %>

&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;* "Infomation Check" testcases check infomation of system, including POST, OS installation, OS, etc.<br>
&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;* All abnormal information will be taken attention to, and be checked if they are bugs.<br>

| Testcase Type&lt;br&gt(where cases are executed) | Testcase Name | Execution Steps |<br>
<% @infochecktestcases.each do |t| %>
| 
	<% if tmptype == nil then %>
		<%= t.casetype.name if t.casetype != nil %>
		<% tmptype = t.casetype %>
	<% else %>
		<%= t.casetype.name if t.casetype != tmptype %>
		<% tmptype = t.casetype %>
	<% end %>
| <%= t.name %> | <%= t.steps.gsub("\n", '<br>') if t.steps != nil %> |<br>
<% end %>


